%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarack-obama-endorses-kamala-harris-for-president-after-a-delay-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721984720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a287bf5a8a7bf0491997ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarack-obama-endorses-kamala-harris-for-president-after-a-delay-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Barack%20Obama%20endorses%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20marking%20a%20pivotal%20moment%20in%20the%202024%20race.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ggoodwin%40businessinsider.com%20(Grace%20Eliza%20Goodwin%2CJoshua%20Nelken-Zitser)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A37%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarack-obama-endorses-kamala-harris-for-president-after-a-delay-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kids%20to%20Senior%20Citizens%2C%20Anyone%20Can%20Use%20This%20Techie%E2%80%99s%20DIY%20Handloom%20Kit%20To%20Weave%20Fabric%20At%20Home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKalaiyarasi%20Ramachandran%20spent%20her%20childhood%20admiring%20the%20large%20handlooms%20in%20the%20quaint%20weavers%E2%80%99%20lanes%20of%20Salangapalayam%20village%20in%20Erode%20district%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20The%20rhythmic%20sound%20of%20looms%20and%20transformation%20of%20yarn%20into%20nine%20yards%20of%20sarees%20diligently%20woven%20by%20the%20weavers%20was%20magical%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20carefully%20watch%20the%20fine%20threads%20being%20woven%20in%20the%20loom.%20We%20would%20fear%20sitting%20near%20the%20weavers%20as%20the%20work%20required%20focus%20and%20no%20distraction.%20I%20would%20be%20tasked%20with%20small%20works%20like%20rotating%20the%20spinning%20wheel.%20We%20did%20not%20have%20a%20%3Cem%3Eraatai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spinning%20wheel)%20in%20our%20house%2C%20so%20I%20would%20sneak%20to%20the%20weavers%E2%80%99%20homes%20and%20admire%20the%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20grew%20up%2C%20Kalaiyarasi%20went%20on%20to%20study%20computer%20science%20and%20secured%20a%20well-paying%20job%20at%20an%20IT%20company%20in%20Chennai%20as%20a%20developer.%20A%20turning%20point%20came%20in%20her%20life%20when%20she%20came%20back%20to%20her%20hometown%20during%20her%20second%20maternity%20leave%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20noticed%20that%20the%20looms%20in%20my%20hometown%20had%20reduced%20from%207%2C500%20to%20only%202%2C500.%20A%20lot%20of%20weavers%20migrated%20to%20other%20industries%20to%20work%20as%20night%20watchmen%2C%20workers%20in%20textile%20mills%2C%20and%20catering%20businesses.%20They%20moved%20to%20cities%20to%20earn%20a%20daily%20wage%20of%20Rs%20150.%20This%20pushed%20the%20community%20into%20poverty%20and%20eventually%20they%20started%20marrying%20off%20their%20girls%20at%20tender%20ages%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FRaatai-1-1721982469.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20her%20startup%20%E2%80%98Raatai%20handlooms%E2%80%99%2C%20Kalaiyarasi%20introduced%20DIY%20handloom%20kits.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FRaatai-1-1721982469.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FRaatai-1-1721982469-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FRaatai-1-1721982469-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FRaatai-1-1721982469-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FRaatai-1-1721982469-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358634%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20her%20startup%20%E2%80%98Raatai%20handlooms%E2%80%99%2C%20Kalaiyarasi%20introduced%20DIY%20handloom%20kits.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20determined%20to%20breathe%20new%20life%20into%20a%20declining%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F308649%2Fanshul-malhotra-krishna-wools-preserves-himachal-handloom-designs-helps-weavers-earn%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehandloom%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20born%20and%20brought%20up%20in%20the%20same%20area%20as%20those%20weavers.%20I%20felt%20like%20doing%20something%20for%20the%20society%20and%20reviving%20this%20art%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKalaiyarasi%20spoke%20to%20weavers%20to%20understand%20the%20gaps%20behind%20this%20waning%20art.%20%E2%80%9CI%20came%20to%20know%20that%20the%20younger%20generations%20do%20not%20want%20to%20engage%20in%20weaving.%20The%20loom%20also%20occupies%20a%20lot%20of%20space%2C%20typically%20taking%206%C3%976%20feet%20area%20in%20the%20room%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2036-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20the%20work%20interesting%20and%20engaging%2C%20she%20manufactured%20DIY%20handloom%20kits%20with%20the%20help%20of%20weavers.%20They%20help%20her%20with%20the%20designs%20and%20assembling%20of%20the%20looms%20with%20the%20process%20taking%20anywhere%20between%202-5%20days.%20Occupying%20less%20space%2C%20it%20can%20be%20used%20by%20anyone%2C%20from%20children%20to%20senior%20citizens%20to%20weave%20fabrics%20from%20yarns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20her%20startup%20%E2%80%98Raatai%20handlooms%E2%80%99%2C%20Kalaiyarasi%20introduced%20three%20kinds%20of%20looms.%20At%20the%20first%20level%20is%20%E2%80%98WeaveMate%E2%80%99%20which%20comes%20with%20a%20loom%20frame%20and%20can%20be%20used%20to%20make%20purses%2C%20wall%20hangings%2C%20mats%2C%20coasters%2C%20and%20pouches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20second%20level%20is%20%E2%80%98WeaveAlly%E2%80%99%20which%20can%20be%20used%20to%20make%20slightly%20bigger%20products%20like%20handbags%2C%20stoles%2C%20scarves%2C%20headbands%2C%20and%20table%20runners.%20At%20the%20third%20level%2C%20she%20has%20%E2%80%98WeaveFit%E2%80%99%20which%20can%20be%20used%20to%20weave%20towels%20and%20handkerchiefs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20DIY%20kits%20come%20along%20with%20a%20user%20manual%20with%20a%20QR%20(Quick%20Response)%20code%20that%20links%20to%20instructional%20videos%2C%20ensuring%20a%20seamless%20learning%20process.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20simply%20scanning%20it%2C%20you%20will%20be%20able%20to%20access%20a%20video%20that%20showcases%20how%20to%20use%20the%20loom.%20It%20is%20so%20easy%20that%20anyone%20can%20design%20their%20fabric%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FRaatai-2-1721982539.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22These%20DIY%20handloom%20kits%20can%20be%20used%20by%20anyone%2C%20from%20children%20to%20senior%20citizens%20to%20weave%20fabrics%20from%20yarns.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FRaatai-2-1721982539.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FRaatai-2-1721982539-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FRaatai-2-1721982539-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FRaatai-2-1721982539-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FRaatai-2-1721982539-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358635%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%