Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShot%20back%20Ms%20Wilson%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bentire%20thing%20was%20made%20up%26quot%3B%2C%20in%20a%20long%20thread%20on%20Threads%2C%20the%20Meta%20micro-blogging%20rival%20to%20her%20father-owned%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20disowned%20him%2C%20not%20the%20other%20way%20around%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%2020-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20shared%20the%20screenshot%20of%20an%20online%20post%20by%20Musk%20that%20claimed%20Wilson%20was%20born%20%26quot%3Bgay%20and%20slightly%20autistic%26quot%3B%20-%20which%20the%20Tesla%20boss%20said%20were%20%26quot%3Battributes%20that%20contribute%20to%20gender%20dysphoria%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20that%20from%20when%20he%20was%20about%204%20years%20old%20and%20he%20would%20pick%20out%20clothes%20for%20me%20to%20wear%20like%20a%20jacket%20and%20tell%20me%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bfabulous!%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20well%20as%20his%20love%20of%20musicals%20%26amp%3B%20theatre.%20But%20he%20was%20not%20a%20girl%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20Musk's%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-text-post-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40vivllainous%2Fpost%2FC91xDGJSUX_%5C%22%20data-text-post-version%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40vivllainous%2Fpost%2FC91xDGJSUX_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40vivllainous%2Fpost%2FC91xDGJSUX_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPost%20by%20%40vivllainous%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40vivllainous%2Fpost%2FC91xDGJSUX_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EView%20on%20Threads%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20entirely%20fake%2C%26quot%3B%20shot%20back%20Wilson.%20%26quot%3BLike%2C%20literally%20none%20of%20this%20ever%20happened.%20Ever.%20I%20don't%20even%20know%20where%20he%20got%20this%20from.%20My%20best%20guess%20is%20that%20he%20went%20to%20the%20Milo%20Yiannopoulis%20school%20of%20gay%20stereotypes%2C%20just%20picked%20some%20at%20random%20and%20said%20%26quot%3Beh-%20good%20enough%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20last-ditch%20attempt%20to%20garner%20sympathy%20points%20when%20he%20is%20so%20obviously%20in%20the%20wrong%20even%20in%20his%20own%20fu**ing%20story.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Wilson%20denied%20that%20she%20ever%20picked%20jackets%20for%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20most%20certainly%20not%20calling%20them%20%26quot%3Bfabulous%26quot%3B%20because%20literally%20what%20the%20f**k.%20I%20did%20not%20use%20the%20word%20fabulous%20when%20I%20was%20four%20because%20once%20again%20I%20would%20like%20to%20reiterate...%20I%20was%20four%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20claimed%20she%20did%20not%20have%20her%20father%20by%20her%20side%20when%20she%20was%20growing%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20entire%20thing%20is%20completely%20made%20up%20and%20there's%20a%20reason%20for%20this.%20He%20doesn't%20know%20what%20I%20was%20like%20as%20a%20child%20because%20he%20quite%20simply%20wasn't%20there%2C%20and%20in%20the%20little%20time%20that%20he%20was%20I%20was%20relentlessly%20harassed%20for%20my%20femininity%20and%20queerness.%20Obviously%20he%20can't%20say%20that%2C%20so%20I've%20been%20reduced%20to%20a%20happy%20little%20stereotype%20f*g-ing%20along%20to%20use%20at%20his%20discretion.%20I%20think%20that%20says%20alot%20about%20how%20he%20views%20queer%20people%20and%20children%20in%20general%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ms%20Wilson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20sought%20to%20clear%20the%20air%20over%20her%20gender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20legally%20recognized%20as%20a%20woman%20in%20the%20state%20of%20California%20and%20I%20don't%20concern%20myself%20with%20the%20opinions%20of%20those%20who%20are%20below%20me.%20Obviously%20Elon%20can't%20say%20the%20same%20be