ot%3B%20including%20arson%20attacks%20that%20have%20disrupted%20the%20transport%20system%2C%20train%20operator%20SNCF%20said%20Friday%2C%20hours%20before%20the%20opening%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Paris%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20source%20close%20to%20the%20investigation%20told%20AFP%20the%20attacks%20were%20coordinated%20acts%20of%20%26quot%3Bsabotage%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20massive%20attack%20on%20a%20large%20scale%20to%20paralyse%20the%20TGV%20network%2C%26quot%3B%20SNCF%20told%20AFP%2C%20adding%20that%20many%20routes%20will%20have%20to%20be%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSNCF%20was%20the%20victim%20of%20several%20simultaneous%20malicious%20acts%20overnight%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20national%20train%20operator%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20attacks%20affected%20its%20Atlantic%2C%20northern%20and%20eastern%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArson%20attacks%20were%20started%20to%20damage%20our%20facilities%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20traffic%20on%20the%20affected%20lines%20was%20%26quot%3Bheavily%20disrupted%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20situation%20would%20last%20through%20the%20weekend%20as%20repairs%20are%20conducted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%26quot%3Bmassive%20attack%26quot%3B%20against%20France's%20high-speed%20TGV%20rail%20network%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Boutrageous%20criminal%20act%26quot%3B%2C%20Transport%20Minister%20Patrice%20Vergriete%20said%20Friday%2C%20hours%20ahead%20of%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%20opening%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bvery%20serious%20consequences%26quot%3B%20for%20rail%20traffic%20throughout%20the%20weekend%20with%20connections%20towards%20northern%2C%20eastern%20and%20northwestern%20France%20halved%2C%20Vergriete%20said%2C%20while%20rail%20operator%20SNCF%20chief%20executive%20Jean-Pierre%20Farandou%20said%20800%2C000%20passengers%20were%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrains%20were%20being%20diverted%20to%20different%20tracks%20%26quot%3Bbut%20we%20will%20have%20to%20cancel%20a%20large%20number%20of%20them%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20southeastern%20line%20was%20not%20affected%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20malicious%20act%20was%20foiled%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESNCF%20urged%20passengers%20to%20postpone%20their%20trips%20and%20stay%20away%20from%20train%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOlympics%20under%20heavy%20security%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attacks%20were%20launched%20as%20Paris%20was%20under%20heavy%20security%20ahead%20of%20the%20opening%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Summer%20Olympics%2C%20with%20300%2C000%20spectators%20and%20an%20audience%20of%20VIPs%20expected%20at%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parade%20on%20Friday%20evening%20will%20see%20up%20to%207%2C500%20competitors%20travel%20down%20a%20six-kilometre%20(four-mile)%20stretch%20of%20the%20river%20Seine%20on%20a%20flotilla%20of%2085%20boats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20the%20first%20time%20a%20Summer%20Olympics%20has%20opened%20outside%20the%20main%20athletics%20stadium%2C%20a%20decision%20fraught%20with%20danger%20at%20a%20time%20when%20France%20is%20on%20its%20highest%20alert%20for%20terror%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Paris's%20Montparnasse%20train%20station%2C%20dozens%20of%20passengers%20were%20waiting%20for%20more%20information%20about%20their%20trips%20after%20delays%20of%2030%20minutes%20to%20almost%20two%20hours%20were%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNormal%20traffic%20is%20expected%20to%20resume%20on%20Monday%2C%20July%2029%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20one%20of%20the%20signs%20in%20the%20departure%20hall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20arrived%20around%207%3A00%20am%20but%20we%20were%20told%20that%20we%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20leave%20before%20Monday%2C%26quot%3B%20said%2027-year-old%20student%20Jocelyn%2C%20who%20had%20planned%20to%20travel%20to%20Bretagne%20and%20refused%20to%20give%20her%20full%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26q