to%20mention%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20the%20Agniveers%20once%20they%20retire%20after%20a%20four-year%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPM%20is%20saying%20that%20we%20are%20spreading%20confusion.%20He%20is%20speaking%20about%20what%20will%20happen%20after%2030%20years.%20He%20should%20talk%20about%20what%20will%20after%204%20years%20to%20these%20agniveers%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Randhawa%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%202022%2C%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%20was%20designed%20to%20recruit%20personnel%20for%20short-term%20service%20in%20the%20armed%20forces%2C%20aimed%20at%20reducing%20the%20age%20profile%20across%20the%20services.%20Known%20as%20Agniveers%2C%20these%20individuals%20do%20not%20currently%20qualify%20for%20regular%20benefits%20such%20as%20pensions%20for%20their%20families%20in%20the%20event%20of%20their%20death%20in%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20has%20sparked%20broader%20discussions%2C%20with%20a%20parliamentary%20panel%20earlier%20recommending%20that%20families%20of%20Agniveers%20who%20die%20in%20the%20line%20of%20duty%20should%20receive%20benefits%20equivalent%20to%20those%20provided%20to%20families%20of%20regular%20military%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20PM%20Modi%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20spreading%20lies%20about%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%20to%20ensure%20that%20youths%20do%20not%20sign%20up%20for%20short-term%20recruitment%20in%20the%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(Congress)%20did%20not%20want%20our%20defence%20forces%20to%20have%20the%20latest%20fighter%20planes.%20They%20are%20opposing%20the%20Agnipath%20Scheme%20which%20is%20aimed%20at%20making%20our%20soldiers%20young%20and%20fighting%20fit%20for%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20the%20Kargil%20War%20memorial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20saying%20that%20the%20Agniveer%20Scheme%20has%20been%20floated%20to%20save%20on%20pensions%20by%20Narendra%20Modi.%20They%20forget%20that%20a%20soldier%20recruited%20today%20will%20be%20eligible%20for%20a%20pension%20after%2030%20years%20and%20by%20then%20Modi%20would%20be%20105.%20They%20want%20people%20to%20believe%20that%20Modi%20is%20such%20a%20fool%20that%20he%20will%20play%20mischief%20with%20the%20country's%20defence%20forces%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20huge%20row%20broke%20out%20earlier%20this%20month%20with%20the%20family%20of%20Agniveer%20Ajay%20Kumar%2C%20who%20died%20in%20the%20line%20of%20duty%2C%20demanding%20'hero'%20status%20for%20him.%20The%20family%20said%20that%20the%20compensation%20money%20cannot%20replace%20Ajay%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721979540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F7d0c2ue_agniveer-scheme_625x300_13_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-kargil-war-diwas-pm-modi-vs-congress-over-agnipath-agniveer-scheme-6192021%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%2225th%20Kargil%20Vijay%20Diwas%3A%20Congress%20leader%20Karti%20Chidambaram%20criticised%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20defending%20the%20'Agnipath'%20scheme%20at%20an%20event%20to%20honour%20the%20Kargil%20War%20soldiers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-kargil-war-diwas-pm-modi-vs-congress-over-agnipath-agniveer-scheme-6192021%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-kargil-war-diwas-pm-modi-vs-congress-over-agnipath-agniveer-scheme-6192021%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-kargil-war-diwas-pm-modi-vs-congress-over-agnipath-agniveer-scheme-6192021%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Can't%20force%20anyone%20to%20disclose%20names'%3A%20SC%20stay%20on%20kanwar%20yatra%20order%20to%20continue%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721979466000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112036728