%20body%2C%20if%20the%20femur%20were%20to%20break%20it%20would%20essentially%20mean%20death.%20But%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20bone%20showed%20healing%20meant%20that%20someone%20had%20cared%20for%20this%20person%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhavana%20elaborates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKnow%20about%20caregiver%20depression%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Bhavana%E2%80%99s%20dad%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20multiple%20system%20atrophy%20%E2%80%94%20a%20condition%20notorious%20for%20tremors%2C%20autonomic%20dysfunction%2C%20and%20the%20muscle%20rigidity%20it%20causes%2C%20she%20experienced%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20grief%20%E2%80%94%20anticipatory%20grief%3B%20a%20grief%20for%20the%20inevitable%20reality.%20Today%2C%20the%20spectrum%20of%20feelings%20(including%20hopelessness)%20comes%20under%20the%20umbrella%20of%20caregiver%20depression.%20%E2%80%9CStudies%20say%20there%20is%20a%20very%20strong%20correlation%20between%20death%20by%20suicide%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F174771%2Fcaregiver-burnout-mental-health-disorders-awareness-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecaregiving%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebecause%20both%20feel%20like%20you%E2%80%99re%20dealing%20with%20something%20hopeless%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bhavana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20look%20to%20cure%20anything%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20helped%20Bhavana%20was%20when%2C%20instead%20of%20looking%20at%20her%20caregiving%20as%20a%20way%20of%20healing%20the%20person%20(which%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20possible)%2C%20she%20began%20to%20see%20it%20as%20a%20way%20of%20helping%20them.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20important%20that%20the%20person%20you%E2%80%99re%20caring%20for%20should%20have%20a%20full%20life.%20You%20have%20to%20remember%20that%20what%20we%20are%20doing%20is%20adding%20life%20to%20their%20days%20and%20not%20the%20other%20way%20around.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20the%20purpose%20of%20life%20is