3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAn%20idea%20to%20resolve%20year-long%20disputes%20online%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Vikram%20pursued%20higher%20education%20in%20computer%20science%2C%20Pranjal%20and%20Akshetha%20studied%20law.%20In%202015%2C%20Vikram%20and%20Pranjal%2C%20who%20was%20then%20a%20second-year%20law%20student%20at%20the%20West%20Bengal%20National%20University%20of%20Juridical%20Sciences%2C%20met%20at%20the%20Startup%20Weekend%20event%20hosted%20by%20IIM-Calcutta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20of%20us%20came%20with%20a%20startup%20idea.%20I%20envisioned%20working%20on%20an%20Online%20Dispute%20Resolution%20(ODR)%20system%20that%20could%20reduce%20the%20dependency%20on%20courts%20which%20are%20already%20burdened%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F34596%2Fsupreme-court-launches-portal-to-track-pending-cases%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebacklog%20of%20cases%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pranjal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20he%20got%20JAMS%20Weinstein%20International%20Fellowship%20opportunity%20as%20part%20of%20which%20he%20attended%20the%20mediation%20training%20course%20at%20Harvard%20Law%20School%20and%20the%20Business%20Development%20Course%20at%20the%20Stanford%20Graduate%20Business%20School.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20always%20fond%20of%20mediation.%20This%20three-month%20long%20fellowship%20allowed%20me%20to%20observe%20the%20online%20dispute%20resolution%20and%20case%20management%20concepts%20in%20the%20US.%20Back%20at%20home%20in%20India%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Etareekh-pe-tareekh%20%3C%2Fem%3E(chronic%20delay%20in%20judicial%20proceedings)%20hinders%20justice.%20I%20wanted%20to%20reduce%20the%20burden%20on%20courts%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Pranjal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20the%20trio%20launched%20Sama%20%E2%80%93%20meaning%20to%20ask%20and%20advise%20others.%20Sama%20is%20based%20on%20%3Cem%3Esaam%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%8