s%20offerings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrilliant%20and%20unique%20though%20each%20menu%20is%20%E2%80%94%20a%20fact%20that%20owes%20to%20their%20owners%E2%80%99%20cultural%20roots%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20South%20Asia%20%E2%80%94%20the%20restaurants%20at%20Curry%20Mile%20are%20bound%20by%20a%20single%20promise%3A%20to%20serve%20you%20the%20best%20%3Cem%3Echicken%20tikka%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E.%20So%2C%20have%20a%20seat%20while%20we%20regale%20you%20with%20the%20vibrant%20(and%20debatable)%20origins%20of%20one%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F326173%2Forigins-of-iconic-indian-dishes-loved-across-the-world-food-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehistory%E2%80%99s%20most%20loved%20dishes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20640px)%20100vw%2C%20640px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F36869943_2009599892410608_4959226096185769984_n-1721034983.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20chicken%20tikka%20masala%20is%20a%20popular%20dish%20in%20both%2C%20India%20and%20the%20UK%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F36869943_2009599892410608_4959226096185769984_n-1721034983.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F36869943_2009599892410608_4959226096185769984_n-1721034983-300x240.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F36869943_2009599892410608_4959226096185769984_n-1721034983-500x400.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F36869943_2009599892410608_4959226096185769984_n-1721034983-150x120.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356875%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20chicken%3Cem%3E%20tikka%20masala%3