%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20adds%20that%20the%20selection%20rate%20in%20civil%20services%20is%20about%200.1%20percent%2C%20so%20even%20the%20best%20candidates%20have%20a%20high%20probability%20of%20not%20making%20the%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThinking%20in%20your%20early%20twenties%20that%20you%20will%20do%20whatever%20it%20takes%20to%20become%20an%20IAS%20officer%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20many%20years%20it%20takes%2C%20might%20sound%20courageous.%20But%20if%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20work%20out%2C%20and%20you%E2%80%99ve%20spent%20six%20to%20seven%20years%20preparing%20for%20UPSC%2C%20it%20becomes%20very%20hard%20to%20do%20something%20else%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20to%20transitioning%20to%20a%20different%20career%20was%20not%20a%20smooth%20one%20for%20either%20Jigyasu%20or%20Akshat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkshat%20had%20harboured%20a%20dream%20of%20becoming%20a%20civil%20servant%20since%20Class%209.%20He%20completed%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20economics%2C%20worked%20for%20a%20year%20and%20resigned%20to%20focus%20on%20UPSC%20exams.%20After%20two%20unsuccessful%20attempts%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20return%20to%20a%20corporate%20career.%20Both%20brothers%20recall%20reaching%20out%20to%20friends%2C%20college%20mates%2C%20former%20colleagues%20and%20ex-UPSC%20aspirants.%20To%20their%20dismay%2C%20none%20of%20them%20really%20helped%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20reached%20out%20to%20hundreds%20of%20people%20and%20applied%20to%20hundreds%20of%20organisations.%20Very%20few%20were%20kind%20enough%20to%20respond.%20What%20I%20struggled%20with%20was%20finding%20my%20niche.%20Deciding%20an%20alternate%20career%20was%20difficult%20as%20I%20was%20an%20engineer%20by%20education%2C%20who%20worked%20in%20business%20strategy%20and%20later%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20policy%20and%20politics%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jigyasu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20narrowing%20down%20on%20public%20policy%20and%20political%20consulting%20as%20areas%20of%20interest%2C%20he%20spent%20about%20six%20months%20upskilling%20himself%20through%20online%20courses%20like%20Coursera%20and%20YouTube%20videos.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202023%2C%20he%20secured%20a%20job%20in%20a%20political%20consultancy%20firm.%20When%20the%20two%20brothers%20met%20after%20this%2C%20the%20conversation%20turned%20heavy%20when%20they%20shared%20experiences%20about%20the%20difficult%20road%20they%20embarked%20on%20to%20reach%20here.%20A%20lack%20of%20guidance%20and%20mentorship%20jarringly%20stood%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20smooth%20transition%20to%20a%20corporate%20career%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20attempt%20to%20create%20impact%2C%20the%20duo%20launched%20Rebounce%20in%20October%202023.%20The%20social%20enterprise%20aims%20to%20render%20robust%20support%20to%20fellow%20aspirants%20transitioning%20from%20UPSC%20preparations%20to%20alternative%20fulfilling%20careers.%20Its%20mission%20is%20crafted%20around%20offering%20these%20individuals%20a%20%E2%80%98second%20chance%E2%80%99%20by%20opening%20doors%20to%20numerous%20opportunities%20and%20guiding%20them%20towards%20satisfying%20career%20paths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Ashare%3A7218026798205321216%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221256%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGargi%20(25)%20worked%20towards%20UPSC%20for%20nearly%20four%20years%20after%20completing%20her%20undergraduate%20degree.%20When%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20clear%20the%20exam%20after%20three%20attempts%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20look%20at%20greener%20pastures.%20But%20what%20they%20would%20be%20remained%20a%20question%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20unsure%20about%20her%20next%20steps%2C%20she%20heard%20about%20Rebounce.%20She%20reached%20out%20and%20received%20a%20mentorship%20session%20from%20Akshat%20and%20Jigyasu.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20very%20confused%20about%20what%20path%20to%20take%20next.%20While%20I%20was%20interested%20in%20the%20development%20sector%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20get%20in%2C%20which%20NGOs%20to%20apply%20to%2C%20which%20fellowships%20I%20should%20aim%20for.%20I%20had%20nobody%20to%20guide%20me.%20Rebounce%20helped%20me%20by%20charting%20a%20path%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJigyasu%20explains%20that%20when%20an%20ex-UPSC%20aspirant%20approaches%20them%2C%20they%20first%20conduct%20a%20free%20mentorship%20session%20to%20help%20them%20envision%20a%20path.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20biggest%20question%20in%20most%20of%20their%20minds%20is%20what%20to%20do%20next%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERebounce%20helps%20them%20by%20understanding%20their%20interests%2C%20aspirations%20and%20skills.%20Based%20on%20these%2C%20they%20give%20them%20certain%20options%20for%20possible%20careers.%20Their%20flagship%20market%20readiness%20programme%20offers%20support%20at%20five%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESupport%20provided%20by%20Rebounce%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Col%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20to%20do%20next%3A%20Decided%20based%20on%20skills%2C%20aspirations%2C%20and%20interests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOne-on-one%20guidance%3A%20Co-founders%20guide%20candidates%20with%20whatever%20doubts%20they%20have.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUpskilling%3A%20Courses%20and%20upskilling%20programmes%20to%20bridge%20skill%20gaps.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPortfolio%20building%3A%20Projects%2C%20fellowships%2C%20and%20volunteering%20to%20gain%20hands-on%20experience.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBuilding%20a%20Resume%2FLinkedIn%20Profile%3A%20Creating%20an%20industry-recognised%20resume%20and%20compelling%20cover%20letter.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EInterview%20readiness%3A%20Preparing%20candidates%20to%20convert%20their%20skills%20into%20jobs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECorporate%20referrals%3A%20Connecting%20candidates%20through%20a%20professional%20network.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20Rebounce%20has%20helped%20over%20300%20former%20UPSC%20aspirants%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20now%20working%20in%20public%20policy%2C%20impact%20consulting%2C%20NGOs%20and%20other%20corporates%2C%20shares%20Jigyasu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20enterprise%20mainly%20helps%20ex-aspirants%20showcase%20the%20skills%20they%20bring%20to%20the%20table.%20Jigyasu%20opines%20that%20the%20market%20does%20not%20recognise%20the%20unique%20skills%20that%20an%20ex-UPSC%20aspirant%20has.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInstead%20of%20looking%20at%20it%20as%20a%20blank%20gap%20of%20four%20to%20five%20years%2C%20recruiters%20should%20look%20at%20the%20skills%20that%20preparing%20for%20this%20exam%20builds%20in%20you.%20These%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311132%2Fmother-daughter-sustainable-lifestyle-brand-helps-homemakers-earn-bags-shark-tank-deal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecandidates%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20transferable%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20include%20resilience%2C%20persistence%2C%20hard%20work%2C%20perseverance%2C%20holistic%20thinking%20and%20much%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20506px)%20100vw%2C%20506px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-13-at-17.31.31-1721385483.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22506%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jigyasu%20Agarwal.%20Co-founder%2C%20Rebounce%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-13-at-17.31.31-1721385483.jpeg%20506w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-13-at-17.31.31-1721385483-300x247.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-13-at-17.31.31-1721385483-500x411.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-13-at-17.31.31-1721385483-150x123.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357671%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22416%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJigyasu%20Agarwal.%20Co-founder%2C%20Rebounce%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20their%20market%20readiness%20programme%2C%20which%20is%20paid%2C%20Rebounce%20also%20conducts%20free%20webinars%20and%20master%20classes%20on%20public%20policy%2C%20impact%20consulting%2C%20political%20consulting%2C%20the%20development%20sector%2C%20resume%20writing%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20also%20started%20a%20podcast%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98Plan%20B%20Diaries%E2%80%99%20where%20they%20speak%20to%20successful%20ex-UPSC%20aspirants%20who%20now%20work%20in%20places%20like%20the%20World%20Bank.%20They%20plan%20to%20launch%20upskilling%20courses%20soon.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETheir%20aim%20is%20to%20help%20aspirants%20shine%20in%20any%20boardroom.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20fighting%20in%20boardrooms%20of%20various%20organisations%20by%20explaining%20what%20we%20bring%20to%20the%20table%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jigyasu%20emphatically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20wants%20ex-UPSC%20aspirants%20to%20realise%20that%20this%20exam%20is%20a%20means%20and%20not%20an%20end.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20start%20your%20civil%20services%20preparation%2C%20have%20a%20number%20of%20attempts%20in%20your%20mind.%20If%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20make%20it%2C%20find%20another%20path%20to%20reach%20your%20final%20goal.%20We%20are%20here%20to%20support%20you%20in%20making%20a%20smooth%20transition%20to%20a%20satisfying%20and%20fulfilling%20career%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGargi%2C%20who%20secured%20positions%20in%20two%20well-known%20fellowships%2C%20Teach%20For%20India%20and%20SBI%2